script.name: plugin.guilds.createpassenger
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds' $guild.data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' $guild.config = get global variable: name='guilds.config'
skip if $guild.data return null
if not $a.guild $a.guild = $guild.data['taxi'] end
skip if $a.guild return null
$current.time = playing time if not $a.ignoreTime $last.time = $a.guild['last.create'] if $last.time $wait.time = $guild.config['passenger.create.wait'] skip if $wait.time $wait.time = 30 if ( $last.time + $wait.time ) > $current.time return null end end end
$tPassengers = $a.guild['passengers'] if not $tPassengers $tPassengers = table alloc $a.guild['passengers'] = $tPassengers end
* valid passenger races $passenger.races = table alloc $passenger.races[Argon] = [TRUE] $passenger.races[Boron] = [TRUE] $passenger.races[Split] = [TRUE] $passenger.races[Paranid] = [TRUE] $passenger.races[Teladi] = [TRUE] $passenger.races[Terran] = [TRUE] $passenger.races[Yaki] = [TRUE] $passenger.races[Pirates] = [TRUE]
* valid sectors @ $main.universe = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.utils : type='mainUniverse' Value1=null Value 2=null skip if $main.universe -> exists $main.universe = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=0 skip if $main.universe -> exists $main.universe = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get sector $available.sectors = table alloc
$aSectors = $main.universe -> find all sectors within 100 jumps: Only known sectors=[FALSE] skip if $aSectors return null
$max.passengers = $guild.config['max.passenger.sector'] skip if $max.passengers $max.passengers = 0
$guild.hq = $a.guild['hq']['obj'] if $guild.hq -> exists $guild.hq.sector = $guild.hq -> get sector end
$i = size of array $aSectors while $i dec $i = $sector = $aSectors[$i] $tPassengers.Sector = $tPassengers[$sector] @ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.interrupt :
* remove any expired if $tPassengers.Sector $key = get next key: table=$tPassengers.Sector key=null while $key @ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.interrupt : $passenger.name = $key $key = get next key: table=$tPassengers.Sector key=$key
$passenger.data = $tPassengers.Sector[$passenger.name] $expire = $passenger.data['expire'] $status = $passenger.data['status'] if $status == 1 AND $current.time > $expire remove key $passenger.name from table $tPassengers.Sector end end end
if $sector != $guild.hq.sector $sector.owner = $sector -> get owner race skip if $passenger.races[$sector.owner] continue
$tDocks = $sector ->get dock table from sector skip if $tDocks continue
@ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.interrupt :
$found = [FALSE] $key = get next key: table=$tDocks key=null while $key if $key -> is of class Trading Dock $found = [TRUE] break end if $key -> is of class Pirate Dock $found = [TRUE] break end $key = get next key: table=$tDocks key=$key end
skip if $found continue end
if not $tPassengers.Sector $available.sectors[$sector] = [TRUE] else $size = size of table $tPassengers.Sector if $size < $max.passengers $available.sectors[$sector] = [TRUE] end end end
skip if size of table $available.sectors return null
$sector = get random key: table=$available.sectors skip if $sector -> exists return null
$tPassengers.Sector = $tPassengers[$sector] if not $tPassengers.Sector $tPassengers.Sector = table alloc $tPassengers[$sector] = $tPassengers.Sector end
$new.passenger = table alloc $new.passenger['sector'] = $sector $sector.owner = $sector -> get owner race $new.passenger['race'] = $sector.owner if random value from 0 to 2 - 1 $text = get random name: race=$sector.owner, female=[FALSE] else $text = get random name: race=$sector.owner, female=[TRUE] end $new.passenger['name'] = $text
$rnd = random value from 0 to 100 - 1 if $rnd >= 90 $type = 5 else if $rnd >= 75 $type = 4 else if $rnd >= 60 $type = 3 else if $rnd >= 25 $type = 2 else $type = 1 end $new.passenger['type'] = $type if $type == 5 $new.passenger['cabin'] = Executive Cabin else if $type == 4 $new.passenger['cabin'] = Luxury Cabin else if $type == 3 $new.passenger['cabin'] = Family Cabin else if $type == 2 $new.passenger['cabin'] = Standard Cabin else $new.passenger['cabin'] = Budget Cabin end
$min = 1 $max = 100 $rnd = random value from 0 to 100 - 1 * Joyride if $rnd >= 90 $xp = random value from 100 to 120 - 1 $travel.type = 4 $min.dest = 0 $table = table alloc $new.passenger['visited'] = $table $rnd = random value from 10 to 31 - 1 $new.passenger['max.visit'] = $rnd $pay = random value from 20000 to 35000 - 1 $pay = $pay * $rnd
* Tourist else if $rnd >= 70 $travel.type = 3 $rnd = random value from 5 to 11 - 1 $xp = random value from 50 to 100 - 1 $pay = random value from 15000 to 30000 - 1 $min = 5 gosub sub.GetSectors
$destination = table alloc while $rnd dec $rnd = $tmp = get random key: table=$tSectors remove key $tmp from table $tSectors $destination[$tmp] = [TRUE] skip if size of table $tSectors break end
$min.dest = 2 $new.passenger['destination'] = $destination $rnd = size of table $destination $pay = $pay * $rnd
* Multiple Destination else if $rnd >= 40 $travel.type = 2 $pay = random value from 18000 to 32000 - 1 $rnd = random value from 3 to 6 - 1 $min = 5 gosub sub.GetSectors $xp = random value from 50 to 100 - 1
$destination = table alloc while $rnd $tmp = get random key: table=$tSectors remove key $tmp from table $tSectors gosub sub.GetStation if $station dec $rnd = $destination[$station] = $station end skip if size of table $tSectors break end $new.passenger['destination'] = $destination
$rnd = size of table $destination $min.dest = 2 $pay = $pay * $rnd
* Single Destination else $xp = random value from 30 to 50 - 1 $pay = random value from 30000 to 65000 - 1 $travel.type = 1 $min.dest = 1 $min = 8 gosub sub.GetSectors while size of table $tSectors $tmp = get random key: table=$tSectors remove key $tmp from table $tSectors gosub sub.GetStation if $station $new.passenger['destination'] = $station break end end end
if $min.dest > 0 $destination = $new.passenger['destination'] $dest.count = 0 if is datatype[ $destination ] == DATATYPE_TABLE $dest.count = size of table $destination else do if $destination -> exists $dest.count = 1 end
if $min.dest > $dest.count $a.guild['last.create'] = $current.time return null end end
$new.passenger['travel.type'] = $travel.type $pay = ( $pay * $type ) + ( $type * 50000 ) $new.passenger['pay'] = $pay $xp = $xp * $type $new.passenger['xp'] = $xp $new.passenger['status'] = 1 $new.passenger['location'] = $sector
$time = random value from 7200 to 14400 - 1 $time = $current.time + $time $new.passenger['expire'] = $time
$text = $new.passenger['name'] $tPassengers.Sector[$text] = $new.passenger
$a.guild['last.create'] = $current.time
return null
sub.GetSectors: @ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.interrupt : $tSectors = table alloc $aSectors = $main.universe -> find all sectors within $max jumps: Only known sectors=[FALSE] $i = size of array $aSectors while $i dec $i = $tmp = $aSectors[$i] $tmp.owner = $tmp -> get owner race do if $tmp.owner -> is aggressive race continue
skip if $passenger.races[$sector.owner] continue
$jumps = get jumps from sector $sector to sector $tmp if $jumps >= $min $tSectors[$tmp] = $jumps end end endsub
sub.GetStation: $station = null if $tmp -> exists @ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.interrupt : $table = $tmp ->get dock table from sector if $table $table.random = table alloc $s = get next key: table=$table key=null while $s $s.owner = $s -> get owner race if not $s.owner -> is aggressive race if $s -> is of class Trading Dock $station = $s endsub end if $passenger.races[$s.owner] $table.random[$s] = [TRUE] end end $s = get next key: table=$table key=$s end if size of table $table.random $station = get random key: table=$table.random remove key $station from table $table.random $s.owner = $station -> get owner race while $s.owner -> is aggressive race $station = get random key: table=$table.random $s.owner = $station -> get owner race remove key $station from table $table.random skip if size of table $table.random break end endsub end end $table = $tmp ->get factory table from sector if $table $table.random = table alloc $s = get next key: table=$table key=null while $s $s.owner = $s -> get owner race if not $s.owner -> is aggressive race if $passenger.races[$s.owner] $table.random[$s] = [TRUE] end end $s = get next key: table=$table key=$s end if size of table $table.random $station = get random key: table=$table.random remove key $station from table $table.random $s.owner = $station -> get owner race while $s.owner -> is aggressive race @ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.interrupt : $station = get random key: table=$table.random $s.owner = $station -> get owner race remove key $station from table $table.random skip if size of table $table.random break end endsub end end end endsub
return null
